Title : Brooklyn Nets accomplishments and records
Text : {{refimprove|date=May 2014}}
{{Use mdy dates|date=April 2019}}
The [[Brooklyn Nets]] are an [[Major North American professional sports teams|American professional]] [[basketball]] [[Professional sports league organization|franchise]] based in [[Brooklyn]], [[New York (state)|New York]]. The team plays in the [[Atlantic Division (NBA)|Atlantic Division]] of the [[Eastern Conference (NBA)|Eastern Conference]] in the [[National Basketball Association]] (NBA).

{{TOClimit|limit=3}}

